        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Based on municipal incinerated PV (hard coal ash incineration PV was calculated as: based on coal usage in residences and small commerce (Exxon 2012), generic split into hard coal and lignite based on demand 2010 (WCA 2012), generic hard coal ash content, and a generic global rate of 21.7w% of MSW going to incineration (Pike + UNSD 2012)). The values for "treatment of hard coal ash, sanitary landfill" is adjusted for the generic global rate of 67w% MSW sent to landfill (UNSD 2011)(http://unstats.un.org/unsd/environment/wastetreatment.htm, accessed 20151008)</productionVolumeComment>
